<br>
Well first off, there is nothing liberal about my opposition to the death penalty.  As far as I'm concerned, the relatively peaceful death (by peaceful I mean you are given ample time to prepare for it, come to terms with it, say goodbye to your loved ones, find Jesus if that's your thing) is hardly compensation for suddenly and brutally ripping away the life of another human being without warning or reason.  If the death penalty was truly equal compensation, it would mean having the offender left free and stalking them, only to kill them as brutally as they killed without warning.  Obviously, that's neither practiacal nor safe for the general public.<br>
<br>
As I stated before, criminals need to be kept in prisons of punishment, not luxury.  My idealist vision would be making them all sleep in the same room with trap door long underwear and 24 hours of Barry Manilow piped in.  And they get just that room - no tv, no computers, no personal belongings, nothing not required for basic survival.  Let them receive mail by letter only, and have it read to them by someone else.  And, let the penalty for any prison employee caught smuggling contraband into the prison be a bed of their own in the room instead of a slap on the wrist and a transfer.<br>
<br>
As for your attempt to bring the Taliban into this.  Think about what you are saying.  You want to punish people who believe that the greatest achievement one can reach in life is to die as a martyr to their sick, twisted cause, after which they will go to &quot;heaven&quot; where they will spend eterinity filled with priveledge and honor, by killing them.  How is killing someone who thinks that way a fitting punishment?  It's more like a reward.  If you want to punish them, send them to a prison with female guards, assign them to a female case worker, and put them in a situation where they are powerless.  The cruellest thing you can do to them is sentance them to a life of mediocrity and obscurity.  The hardest part of imprisoning these fools will be keeping the other inmates from killing them ala Jeffery Dahmer.  <p><img src=http://www.kaseyspace.com/EQ/nenasig.jpg align=center>
